itl.enabler.api

Class PumpCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • itl.enabler.api.PumpCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Pump>

    public class PumpCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Pump>
    A collection of Pump objects

    Note : The collection of Pumps can be iterated with the foreach statement or accessed directly by its index or by the Pump number key.
    Events for all the Pumps can also be accessed via this collection

    See Also:
    Pump

      Event adapter for the PumpCollection class
      static interface  PumpCollection.PumpCollectionEventListener
      Listens to events from every Pump in the collection.
      Clients can either implement this interface to receive events on the whole Pump Collection or subscribe to events from individual pumpsByNum.
